Police in Nairobi are investigating the mysterious deaths of an 84- year-old man and his worker in a house in Pangani. The master, identified as Shudesh Kumar, was found dead on Tuesday in the dinning room of his house. The body of his long-serving domestic worker, identified as 45-year-old Leonard Musembi, was found hanging from the ceiling of a store in the same house. The house was destroyed by a fire this afternoon. Police said the cause of the fire was yet to be established. Click here for the latest political news